enhanced_by.reason: The setupTags method initializes the Tags map, which is used in the hashCode method to determine if a tag is known.
The valueOf method creates Tag objects, which are used in the hashCode method to compute the hash code.
The equals method checks for equality based on the same fields used in the hashCode method, making it a good candidate for asserting the hash code's correctness.
The normalName method accesses the normalName field, which is one of the fields used in the hashCode method.
